
'''Harriet Dansowaa Bruce-Annan''' (N'awoo din ne: '''Grace Akosua Dansowaa Ani-Agyei'''; wɔ woo no afe 1965 wo [[Nkran|Accra]], [[Ghana]]) yɛ Ghanani a n'adwuma ne sɛ ɔnam  abɛforo kwan so hyehyɛ mfidie na afei nso, ɔnsan nso yɛ ohummɔborɔfoɔ a ɔte Dusseldorf, Germany. Wonnim no sɛ adwumakuo African Angel a ɛyɛ adɔyɛ kuo  a ɛboa mmɔfra a wɔn  wɔ ahiafo atenae a ewo Bukom mpɔtam  no hyehyɛfo.

== N'asetenam ne Nnwuma ==
Wɔ woo Bruce-Annan wɔ Accra,afe 1965 mu. Wɔtetee no wɔ Adabraka, na daa nyinaa na ɔkɔ ne nana a na ɔte ahiafoɔ tenabea bi a wɔfrɛ no Bukuom no hɔ nsrahwɛ. ɛmfa ho ɔbrɛ ne ɔhaw ɔfaa mu wɔ ne mmɔfrase no, w'ammu ne mmɔfrase abonfia. Denam mmoa a onya firii ne wɔfa hɔ no, osuaa sɛnea wɔnam abɛɛforo so hyehyɛ dwumadie anaa mfidie wɔ Ghana. Adwumakuo a odikan nyaa mu akwanya no yɛ Germanyfoɔ kɔmputa adwumakuo. Wɔ afe 19990 mu no, bre a ne kunu ka kyerɛɛ  no sɛ ɔbɛboa no ama w'anya suapɔn mu akwanya wɔ amanɔne no, ɔne tu kɔtenaa Germany.Nanso, esiane ateetee a na ɔfa mu wɔ awareɛ mu nti, oguane kɔɔ mmaa guankɔbea a ɛwɔ Dusseldorf. Adwuma a odikan yɛe wɔ hɔ ne sɛ, na ɔyɛ apɔwmudensohwefo boafo, akyire ɔkɔyɛɛ adwuma wɔ yaanee so wɔ Düsseldorf fair na afei, nsanombea a ɛde Golden Unicorn pub wɔ  Ratinger Straße. Bre ɔda so wɔ Dusseldorf no, ɔhyɛɛ ase gyegyee sika de kɔboaa nnyanka a wɔn wɔ ahiafo atenae a ɛwɔ Bukuom, wɔ Accra. Wɔ September da a ɛtɔ  so 15, afe 2002 mu no, Bruce-Annan ne afoforo nsia hyehyɛɛ ekuo a ɛde African Angel Association. Ekuo no yɛ nea ɔboa mmɔfra a wɔn wɔ  Bukum wɔ  wɔn sukuu kɔ ne nnwumasua mu. 

Wɔ  afe 2008 mu no, wɔ too nsa frɛɛ Bruce Annan kɔɔ   Berlin Senate ma no de ne nimdeɛ kɔ boa nyiamu a ɛfa amanman mu atukɔtena ho nsɛm. Wɔ  afe 2009 mu no, ɔkɔyɛɛ TV so dwumadie a ɛde NDR na afei nso, dwumadie bi Mark Lanz nso yɛ so. Bruce-Annan akɔ nsrahwɛ wɔ mmeae pii wɔ Germany ne Austria bre a na ɔda ne nnwuma ahorɔw adi no.

== Abasobɔdeɛ ==
Wɔ March da a ɛtɔ so 31, afe 2011 mu no, nhomawa a w'ato din ''Bild der Frau'' at a gala a ɛwɔ Berlin no maa no abasobɔdeɛ a ɛde heroine of everyday life". Sika a ɛda so no yɛ euros no 30,000

Bre a na wɔredi mmaa afofie da a ɛde World Women's Day wɔ March bosome mu, afe 2013 mu no, Germany aban no maa no abasobɔdeɛ a w'ato din Cross of Merit.

